    "summary": "In this transcript, a pregnant user seeks advice on using leftover medications (pseudoephedrine and ciprofloxacin) to treat sinus infection symptoms and fever. The assistant consistently advises against self-medicating with these specific drugs, explains the potential risks to the fetus, and directs the user toward safer alternatives and professional medical consultation.",
